  &lt;span
    
      style=&#34;color: #f1faee&#34;
    &gt;I will not be held responsible for any data loss resulting from selection of the wrong drive. &lt;strong&gt;BE VERY CAREFUL HERE&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;
